{"title":"Getting started","description":"Get started with HashBrown CMS","template":"sectionPage","url":"/getting-started/","sections":[{"value":{"text":"<h2 id=\"dependencies\">Dependencies</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>git</li>\n<li>With Docker:<ul>\n<li>docker</li>\n<li>docker-compose</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Without Docker:<ul>\n<li>node.js</li>\n<li>mongo</li>\n<li>ImageMagick</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"},"schemaId":"richTextSection"},{"value":{"template":"richTextSection","text":"<h2 id=\"download-the-source\">Download the source</h2>\n\n<p>Clone the 'stable' branch using GIT:</p>\n\n<pre><code>git clone https://github.com/HashBrownCMS/hashbrown-cms.git --recursive\n</code></pre>\n"},"schemaId":"richTextSection"},{"value":{"template":"richTextSection","text":"<h2 id=\"get-the-node-js-dependencies\">Get the node.js dependencies</h2>\n\n<p>There are a couple dependencies to get before you can fire up HashBrown. Go into your installation directory and pull them from NPM:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code>cd ./hashbrown-cms\nnpm install\n</code></pre>\n"},"schemaId":"richTextSection"},{"value":{"template":"richTextSection","text":"<h2 id=\"run-it\">Run it</h2>\n<p>Run HashBrown and visit <a href=\"http://localhost:8080\">http://localhost:8080</a> to see it in action.</p>\n<pre><code>npm run start</code></pre><p>Or via Docker:</p>\n<pre><code>npm run start:docker</code></pre>"},"schemaId":"richTextSection"}],"id":"efbd77b7728265a8cce1981981a3ec4f93195595","parentId":"","schemaId":"sectionPage","createDate":"2016-09-15T15:18:34.969Z","updateDate":"2020-01-08T08:58:44.190Z","createdBy":"Unknown","updatedBy":"unknown","sort":1,"language":"en"}